      <title>Package issue</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/eztrackback/forum/general/package_issue</link>
      <description>Hi,&#13;
&#13;
It seems eZ 4.3 or later doesn't support content class package.&#13;
&#13;
To fix this issue :&#13;
 - import this package in eZ 4.2&#13;
 - create a new package from eZ 4.2 (export content class)&#13;
 - finally import the new package in eZ &gt; 4.3&#13;
&#13;
It would be good to update svn repository with a compatible package :)&#13;
&#13;
Thanks</description>
      <author>community@ez.no (Simon Boyer)</author>
      <guid>http://projects.ez.no/eztrackback/forum/general/package_issue</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jun 2011 07:25:01 +0000</pubDate>
